HEADWORD: Hush
<hw>Hush</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Silent; quiet.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Hush</xex> as death.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>hushed</ent>⟦br⟧
